1
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:42,000
Fang Chi.

2
00:00:45,960 --> 00:00:46,960
Fang Chi?

3
00:00:49,480 --> 00:00:50,480
Fang Chi.

4
00:00:52,680 --> 00:00:53,680
Are you scared?

5
00:00:59,600 --> 00:01:00,680
Fang Chi.

6
00:01:01,640 --> 00:01:02,640
Zhang Zhun.

7
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:04,520
You're drunk.

8
00:01:05,680 --> 00:01:07,240
We're not filming now.

9
00:01:10,960 --> 00:01:11,960
Are you scared?

10
00:01:14,800 --> 00:01:15,800
No.

11
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:17,040
I can't.

12
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:18,480
So you want to.

13
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:27,320
Zhang Zhun, wake the fuck up.

14
00:01:27,880 --> 00:01:28,600
I'm Zhen Xin.

15
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:29,760
Not Fang Chi.

16
00:01:40,320 --> 00:01:41,320
Kiss me.

17
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:45,400
Say the next line.

18
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:49,920
Say the line.

19
00:01:52,360 --> 00:01:53,360
Say you need me.

20
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:56,400
I...

21
00:01:58,400 --> 00:01:59,400
need you.

22
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:37,080
[Xie Danyi]

23
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:03,500
"Deep In"
(Episode 3)

24
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:15,880
Hello?

25
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:17,120
Mr. Zhang,

26
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,160
not up yet?

27
00:04:18,400 --> 00:04:19,800
Makeup starts in 30 minutes.

28
00:04:19,840 --> 00:04:20,560
Get up.

29
00:04:20,840 --> 00:04:21,840
Okay, coming!

30
00:04:21,960 --> 00:04:22,480
Mr. Zhang.

31
00:04:22,520 --> 00:04:22,880
Hurry up.

32
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:23,920
Alright.

33
00:05:25,880 --> 00:05:27,200
Say the next line.

34
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:30,800
Say it.

35
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,480
Say you need me.

36
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:43,920
What the hell did I do?

37
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:55,480
I must be crazy memorizing the lines.

38
00:06:56,520 --> 00:06:57,800
What a crazy dream.

39
00:06:59,960 --> 00:07:00,960
Get it together.

40
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:23,480
Danyi?

41
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:25,480
Sorry,

42
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:26,560
I just saw it.

43
00:07:26,960 --> 00:07:28,160
My phone was on silent.

44
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:30,920
I'm leaving.

45
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:34,680
What?

46
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,096
I was in Coconut City last night...

47
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:38,400
calling you all night.

48
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:40,040
You never picked up.

49
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:42,680
I booked an early flight.

50
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:44,120
I'm at the airport now.

51
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:45,320
I'm sorry, Danyi.

52
00:07:45,760 --> 00:07:46,920
Last night's cast dinner...

53
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:48,240
I got too drunk.

54
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:50,960
Why didn't you tell me?

55
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:53,360
Zhang Zhun.

56
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:55,360
I don't know how to say this.

57
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:58,120
I just feel...

58
00:07:59,280 --> 00:08:00,680
I'm losing you.

59
00:08:00,960 --> 00:08:02,120
What are you talking about?

60
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:04,600
Tell me.

61
00:08:05,520 --> 00:08:06,880
Did you meet someone?

62
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:13,840
Who could I meet here?

63
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:16,240
Right

64
00:08:16,840 --> 00:08:18,000
you're on set.

65
00:08:19,280 --> 00:08:20,720
But I can feel it.

66
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:22,960
You're drifting away.

67
00:08:23,840 --> 00:08:24,840
Tell me.

68
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:26,080
Why?

69
00:08:29,840 --> 00:08:30,840
Don't overthink it.

70
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:32,680
I was just...

71
00:08:33,400 --> 00:08:34,400
too deep in character.

72
00:08:37,560 --> 00:08:38,560
Who is it?

73
00:08:38,920 --> 00:08:40,680
Mr. Zhang, can we do your makeup now?

74
00:08:41,760 --> 00:08:42,760
Coming.

75
00:08:43,560 --> 00:08:43,960
Danyi

76
00:08:44,240 --> 00:08:45,280
I need to go makeup now

77
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:47,040
and we start filming today.

78
00:08:47,920 --> 00:08:48,920
Stay safe.

79
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:50,000
Text me when you land.

80
00:09:21,040 --> 00:09:21,480
Mr. Zhang.

81
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:22,920
Mr. Zhang, your clip is still on.

82
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:24,440
Thanks.

83
00:09:24,800 --> 00:09:25,800
No problem.

84
00:09:33,280 --> 00:09:34,280
Mr. Zhen.

85
00:09:34,400 --> 00:09:36,080
Was it you that took me back last night?

86
00:09:39,520 --> 00:09:40,520
Thank you.

87
00:09:40,640 --> 00:09:41,720
I drank too much.

88
00:09:42,040 --> 00:09:43,680
I don't even remember if you were there.

89
00:09:48,800 --> 00:09:49,800
So...

90
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:52,840
I didn't bother you, did I?

91
00:09:54,560 --> 00:09:55,960
You remember nothing?

92
00:09:59,459 --> 00:10:01,326
I didn't do anything
to offend you, did I?

93
00:10:09,280 --> 00:10:10,280
If you can't drink,

94
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:11,440
then drink less from now on.

95
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:14,360
Mr. Zhang.

96
00:10:14,880 --> 00:10:15,880
We need to go.

97
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:16,760
Director's calling.

98
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:17,440
Okay,

99
00:10:17,520 --> 00:10:18,520
let's go.

100
00:10:48,800 --> 00:10:50,120
Linlin, I'll say it again.

101
00:10:50,160 --> 00:10:51,000
Asking your ex

102
00:10:51,040 --> 00:10:52,560
to treat your boyfriend.

103
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:53,600
It's not right.

104
00:10:53,880 --> 00:10:54,880
Charles.

105
00:10:55,160 --> 00:10:56,280
I want this to last.

106
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:58,360
For what we had,

107
00:10:58,400 --> 00:10:59,400
please help me.

108
00:10:59,520 --> 00:11:01,200
Insomnia has many causes.

109
00:11:01,760 --> 00:11:02,800
It may not be mental.

110
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:04,520
Take him to a doctor first.

111
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:06,200
Charles.

112
00:11:06,560 --> 00:11:08,640
His checkup was normal.

113
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:10,240
It's not just insomnia.

114
00:11:10,640 --> 00:11:12,480
He fears the dark, tight spaces,

115
00:11:12,520 --> 00:11:13,640
and even driving.

116
00:11:13,879 --> 00:11:15,439
He even avoids underground parking.

117
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:17,240
He has nightmares too.

118
00:11:17,520 --> 00:11:18,840
I'm out of options.

119
00:11:18,880 --> 00:11:20,120
I wouldn't ask otherwise.

120
00:11:21,840 --> 00:11:23,160
What other symptoms does he have.

121
00:11:23,240 --> 00:11:24,800
He zones out a lot.

122
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:26,120
He drinks every night.

123
00:11:26,560 --> 00:11:27,680
And in the liquor cabinet,

124
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:28,720
I found sleeping pills.

125
00:11:29,040 --> 00:11:30,280
Half of the bottle's gone.

126
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:32,720
Did he drink before?

127
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:34,320
Barely.

128
00:11:34,840 --> 00:11:36,800
Took about two months to finish a bottle of wine.

129
00:11:37,320 --> 00:11:38,520
But now the cabinet

130
00:11:38,560 --> 00:11:39,560
is full of new bottles.

131
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:42,040
How are you two?

132
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:43,480
We...

133
00:11:43,880 --> 00:11:44,880
In every way,

134
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:47,640
We're fine.

135
00:11:48,600 --> 00:11:50,320
Like any normal couple.

136
00:11:51,040 --> 00:11:52,640
It's just that when I asked,

137
00:11:53,280 --> 00:11:54,280
he didn't respond.

138
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:55,960
Charles.

139
00:11:56,120 --> 00:11:57,520
Can he see you today?

140
00:12:01,360 --> 00:12:02,360
Charles.

141
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:06,720
Tell him come after four.

142
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:09,080
That's great! Thank you.

143
00:12:09,640 --> 00:12:10,760
I'll tell him right away.

144
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:12,480
Thank you so much!

145
00:12:12,640 --> 00:12:13,640
His name is...

146
00:12:14,360 --> 00:12:15,360
Gao Zhun.

147
00:12:31,120 --> 00:12:31,640
Dr. Fang,

148
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:32,840
Mr. Gao has arrived.

149
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:35,200
Isn't it too early?

150
00:12:35,920 --> 00:12:37,000
Miss Feng, it's fine.

151
00:12:37,640 --> 00:12:38,640
I booked four.

152
00:12:38,800 --> 00:12:39,800
I can wait.

153
00:12:45,640 --> 00:12:46,640
Come in.

154
00:13:04,640 --> 00:13:05,720
Nice to meet you, Dr. Fang.

155
00:13:05,920 --> 00:13:06,920
Hello, Mr. Gao.

156
00:13:13,800 --> 00:13:14,960
Take a seat. Mr.Gao.

157
00:13:46,440 --> 00:13:47,960
What do you do?

158
00:13:50,640 --> 00:13:51,640
Art investment.

159
00:13:53,520 --> 00:13:54,520
You studied art?

160
00:13:56,760 --> 00:13:57,760
Art management.

161
00:13:58,400 --> 00:13:59,400
I used make prints.

162
00:14:07,440 --> 00:14:09,200
Is there a problem, Mr. Gao?

163
00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:11,720
No.

164
00:14:12,760 --> 00:14:13,760
Not at all.

165
00:14:17,943 --> 00:14:20,036
(Claustrophobia)

166
00:14:20,520 --> 00:14:22,000
You and Linlin are together?

167
00:14:23,920 --> 00:14:25,240
She's my fiancée.

168
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:29,720
She says

169
00:14:30,200 --> 00:14:31,480
you've had insomnia recently.

170
00:14:32,800 --> 00:14:34,000
Have you tried sleeping pills?

171
00:14:36,680 --> 00:14:37,680
Yes.

172
00:14:39,200 --> 00:14:40,200
They don't work well.

173
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:42,000
And I get nightmares.

174
00:14:57,600 --> 00:14:58,600
About what?

175
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:01,000
Me.

176
00:15:03,200 --> 00:15:04,640
Alone in a parking lot.

177
00:15:15,360 --> 00:15:16,360
It's okay.

178
00:15:17,680 --> 00:15:18,680
With me,

179
00:15:19,200 --> 00:15:20,200
you're safe.

180
00:15:22,520 --> 00:15:23,520
S-

181
00:15:25,440 --> 00:15:26,440
Sorry.

182
00:15:27,800 --> 00:15:28,800
You're scared.

183
00:15:32,120 --> 00:15:33,120
No.

184
00:15:34,280 --> 00:15:35,280
It's just...

185
00:15:37,320 --> 00:15:38,520
you're too close.

186
00:15:47,120 --> 00:15:48,120
I can help you.

187
00:15:50,080 --> 00:15:51,080
But first,

188
00:15:53,040 --> 00:15:54,040
you must trust me.

189
00:15:56,240 --> 00:15:57,240
Understand?

190
00:16:03,320 --> 00:16:04,320
Good.

191
00:16:05,840 --> 00:16:06,840
Come on.

192
00:16:07,400 --> 00:16:08,400
Say it with me...

193
00:16:09,080 --> 00:16:10,400
"Okay, Dr. Fang."

194
00:16:17,160 --> 00:16:18,280
Okay, Dr. Fang.

195
00:16:24,920 --> 00:16:25,920
Mr. Gao.

196
00:16:26,600 --> 00:16:27,600
That's all for today.

197
00:16:29,280 --> 00:16:30,280
Okay.

198
00:16:41,600 --> 00:16:42,600
Then, Dr. Fang,

199
00:16:42,920 --> 00:16:43,920
see you next week.

200
00:16:44,040 --> 00:16:45,040
Wait.

201
00:16:55,560 --> 00:16:56,560
Use this on your eyes.

202
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:58,440
They're swollen.

203
00:17:08,520 --> 00:17:09,520
See you next week.

204
00:17:22,640 --> 00:17:25,040
Charles... What's wrong with him?

205
00:17:25,920 --> 00:17:26,920
I'm not sure yet.

206
00:17:29,560 --> 00:17:30,560
But I suspect

207
00:17:32,200 --> 00:17:33,400
it's not just mental.

208
00:17:39,560 --> 00:17:41,160
Any trauma in his past?

209
00:17:42,320 --> 00:17:43,320
Like

210
00:17:43,880 --> 00:17:44,880
Getting robbed.

211
00:17:45,680 --> 00:17:46,680
Getting kidnapped.

212
00:17:47,760 --> 00:17:48,760
I don't know.

213
00:17:49,920 --> 00:17:50,920
I don't know why

214
00:17:50,960 --> 00:17:52,600
he won't tell me.

215
00:17:54,780 --> 00:17:55,800
Charles.

216
00:17:56,080 --> 00:17:57,120
What should I do?

217
00:17:58,000 --> 00:17:59,040
He needs someone.

218
00:18:00,560 --> 00:18:02,240
A very strong guide

219
00:18:03,840 --> 00:18:06,040
to pull him free.

220
00:18:25,600 --> 00:18:26,600
Get in.

221
00:18:26,800 --> 00:18:27,800
I'll drive you.

222
00:18:35,800 --> 00:18:36,800
No need.

223
00:18:36,880 --> 00:18:37,880
I...

224
00:18:38,080 --> 00:18:39,080
I can walk back.

225
00:18:40,320 --> 00:18:41,320
It's close.

226
00:18:41,680 --> 00:18:42,680
He fears the dark.

227
00:18:42,880 --> 00:18:44,800
Tight spaces, and even driving.

228
00:18:45,160 --> 00:18:46,760
He even avoids underground parking.

229
00:18:47,840 --> 00:18:48,840
All right.

230
00:18:49,400 --> 00:18:50,400
Be safe.

231
00:18:50,600 --> 00:18:51,600
See you next week.

232
00:18:53,760 --> 00:18:54,760
Okay.

233
00:18:54,920 --> 00:18:55,920
See you.

234
00:19:01,240 --> 00:19:02,240
But

235
00:19:03,200 --> 00:19:04,200
When you need help.

236
00:19:04,280 --> 00:19:05,280
Call me.

237
00:19:06,920 --> 00:19:08,240
Even at 3 a.m.

238
00:20:10,400 --> 00:20:11,680
So during your childhood,

239
00:20:13,160 --> 00:20:14,480
it was just you and your mother.

240
00:20:16,640 --> 00:20:18,040
Did she have partners?

241
00:20:20,200 --> 00:20:21,200
Yes.

242
00:20:23,360 --> 00:20:24,960
A tall, strong man.

243
00:20:26,400 --> 00:20:27,560
In a similar way to you.

244
00:20:29,360 --> 00:20:30,360
He was kind.

245
00:20:31,600 --> 00:20:32,600
But

246
00:20:34,560 --> 00:20:35,680
then he left.

247
00:20:38,760 --> 00:20:40,240
My mother was hurt.

248
00:20:46,760 --> 00:20:48,560
Would you say she gave
you too much pressure?

249
00:20:50,160 --> 00:20:51,800
She wanted me to make a name for myself.

250
00:20:52,440 --> 00:20:54,040
I knew she was doing it for my own good.

251
00:20:56,160 --> 00:20:57,160
So

252
00:20:58,800 --> 00:21:00,520
I did everything she wanted.

253
00:21:02,480 --> 00:21:03,480
Is this important?

254
00:21:04,520 --> 00:21:05,520
Very important.

255
00:21:06,760 --> 00:21:08,040
I cried a lot as a kid.

256
00:21:11,160 --> 00:21:12,560
Mom made me hold it in.

257
00:21:25,200 --> 00:21:26,200
She said

258
00:21:27,560 --> 00:21:29,440
real men don't act weak.

259
00:21:36,880 --> 00:21:37,880
Good.

260
00:21:38,960 --> 00:21:39,960
You're doing well.

261
00:21:41,440 --> 00:21:42,440
Now,

262
00:21:45,160 --> 00:21:46,360
tell me about your nightmare.

263
00:21:52,960 --> 00:21:53,960
With me,

264
00:21:54,560 --> 00:21:55,560
you're safe.

265
00:21:56,880 --> 00:21:58,240
It's a secret just between us.

266
00:22:03,120 --> 00:22:05,200
Everything you say here

267
00:22:06,640 --> 00:22:08,000
stays private.

268
00:22:09,960 --> 00:22:10,960
As long as

269
00:22:12,280 --> 00:22:13,280
you don't break any laws.

270
00:22:17,960 --> 00:22:19,200
What if I imagined a crime,

271
00:22:20,160 --> 00:22:21,160
but never did it?

272
00:22:23,360 --> 00:22:24,360
Or

273
00:22:26,080 --> 00:22:27,320
what if I'm the victim?

274
00:22:29,560 --> 00:22:30,560
You need to trust me.

275
00:22:31,840 --> 00:22:33,360
Like I trust you.

276
00:22:35,720 --> 00:22:36,880
You'll help me out.

277
00:22:38,600 --> 00:22:39,600
Right?

278
00:22:41,040 --> 00:22:42,040
I will.

279
00:22:49,320 --> 00:22:50,560
Nightmares live in darkness.

280
00:22:51,640 --> 00:22:52,840
Only by entering it

281
00:22:54,520 --> 00:22:55,800
can I read yours.

282
00:22:59,000 --> 00:23:00,160
From now on,

283
00:23:01,120 --> 00:23:02,200
this tie in my hand

284
00:23:03,080 --> 00:23:04,520
will guide you.

285
00:23:04,544 --> 00:23:06,090
[Victim]

286
00:23:10,440 --> 00:23:11,440
Feel it,

287
00:23:13,480 --> 00:23:15,000
and I'll be with you.

288
00:23:18,520 --> 00:23:19,600
When you're ready,

289
00:23:20,960 --> 00:23:22,160
close your eyes.

290
00:23:30,800 --> 00:23:31,800
Good.

291
00:23:32,440 --> 00:23:33,440
Now,

292
00:23:34,680 --> 00:23:36,480
take me to your nightmare.

293
00:23:38,440 --> 00:23:39,440
CUT

294
00:23:45,960 --> 00:23:46,960
Mr. Zhen.

295
00:23:47,240 --> 00:23:48,520
Was that okay?

296
00:23:48,800 --> 00:23:49,800
Great

297
00:23:50,240 --> 00:23:51,240
Very good.

298
00:23:51,880 --> 00:23:52,880
Now,

299
00:23:52,920 --> 00:23:54,016
let's move to the next scene.

300
00:23:54,040 --> 00:23:55,080
Go get changed.

301
00:23:56,600 --> 00:23:57,600
You go first.

302
00:23:57,640 --> 00:23:58,640
I'll have a smoke.

303
00:24:02,760 --> 00:24:03,320
Zhang Zhun,

304
00:24:03,520 --> 00:24:04,600
go change your look,

305
